Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Leak Detection and Repair Market

Leak detection and repair market will reach at an estimated value of USD 26.11 billion by 2028 and grow at a CAGR of 18.20% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Rising oil and gas pipeline in infrastructure is an essential factor driving the aerospace 3D printing materials market.

Leak detection is defined as the process which is specially designed to check whether there is some leakage in the pipe which consists of gases and liquids. Environmental Protection Agency has created many LDAR regulations so that they can prevent the leakage of dangerous gases and liquid from different industries. LDAR program is there whose main function is to repair these leakages from pumps, connector, valves, pipes and others. Some of the common products of the LDAR are vehicle based detector, manned aircraft detector, handheld gas detectors and UAV based detector. There main function is to protect the environment from these hazardous gases and liquids.

Rise in the adoption of natural gas based power plant is a crucial factor accelerating the market growth, also increase in the strict government regulations to restrain methane emission, rise in the demand for operational and safety efficiency among companies, increase in the incidents of oil and gas leakages in pipelines and storage tanks at production facilities and continuous evolving government regulations pertaining to implementation of leak detection systems are the major factors among others boosting the leak detection and repair market. Moreover, rise in the oil and gas exploration and production activities worldwide, increase in the research and development activities and increase in the global oil and natural gas consumption will further create new opportunities for leak detection and repair market in the forecast period mentioned above.

However, retrofitting complications related to some leak detection systems is the major factor among others restraining the market growth, and will further challenge the leak detection and repair market in the forecast period mentioned above.

